Package order

Class Order

java.lang.Object
order.Order
public class Order extends Object
  • Class representing orders of customers
  • The class's main goal is to consolidate all food items and requests by a customer's order so that staff can process the order
  • The object interacts is of "entity" stereotype and interacts with staff, customer and manager when is comes to adding or processing the order
    • Version:
    1.0
